{
  "source_rule_id": "core.combat.other_forms_of_damage",
  "source_note": "Keeper Rulebook Chapter 6 Table III: Other Forms of Damage (p.124). Each injury type is for one incident or one round. Armor does not reduce these sources (p.120).",
